n is, stort de Vlaamse overheid de subsidie in uw portefeuille.</li><li>Nu kunt u de dienstverlener betalen met uw elektronische kmo-portefeuille. Het kan tot 14 kalenderdagen duren vooraleer de betaling wordt uitgevoerd. Voor buitenlandse dienstverleners kan dit langer duren.</li></ul></li></ul><p>U kunt een projectaanvraag stopzetten als u een foutieve aanvraag hebt ingediend of wanneer de prestatie is geannuleerd.</p>"},"@type":"Procedure","order":0}],"websites":[{"naam":{"en-x-generated":"SME portfolio (VLAIO.be)","nl":"Kmo-portefeuille (VLAIO.be)","nl-BE-x-formal":"Kmo-portefeuille (VLAIO.be)","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Kmo-portefeuille (VLAIO.be)"},"url":"https://www.vlaio.be/nl/subsidies-financiering/kmo-portefeuille","@type":"Website","order":0},{"naam":{"en":"Subsidies for entrepreneurs"},"url":"https://www.vlaio.be/nl/andere-doelgroepen/flanders-innovation-entrepreneurship/subsidies-entrepreneurs/subsidies","@type":"Website","order":1}],"financieleVoordelen":[{"beschrijving":{"en-x-generated":"<p>How much <strong>aid</strong> you get depends on the size of your company. The support is limited to a certain maximum amount that you can draw annually. You are free to choose whether to use that amount for advice or training or a combination of the two. Eligible costs through the SME portfolio <strong>always exclude VAT</strong>. You pay the VAT directly to the service provider.</p><ul><li>Small enterprises receive 30% support within the annual support ceiling of EUR 7,500.</li><li>Medium-sized enterprises receive 20% support within the annual support ceiling of 7,500 euro.</li></ul><div data-table><table><tbody><tr><td> </td><td>Training or advice</td></tr><tr><td>Small enterprises</td><td>Aid rate 30%, aid ceiling 7,500 euro (since 1 January 2020)</td></tr><tr><td>Medium-sized enterprises</td><td>aid rate 20%, aid ceiling €7,500 (since 1 January 2020)</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>The <strong>acceptable cost</strong> of a training course is a minimum of EUR 100, excluding VAT. The acceptable cost of an advice is minimum 500 euro, excluding VAT. Travel costs of the training provider and catering costs are acceptable as costs insofar as they are in a functional relationship with the training (catering costs limited to EUR 25/per day per person). Course material costs are eligible if the course material is used exclusively during the training.</p><p>A global subsidy budget is provided annually. Once the provided budget is allocated, you can no longer apply for support through the SME portfolio.</p><p>The support you receive through the SME portfolio is not tax exempt. As proof of your accounts, you can take a print screen of your online file or a copy of the emails you receive from the SME portfolio. The SME wallet service does not provide invoices. An example of <a href=\"https://www.vlaio.be/nl/media/223\">accounting treatment</a> of the aid can be found on the kmo-portefeuille website.</p>","nl":"<p>Hoeveel <strong>steun</strong> u krijgt, is afhankelijk van de grootte van uw onderneming. De steun is beperkt tot een bepaald maximumbedrag dat u jaarlijks kunt opnemen. U kunt vrij kiezen of u dat bedrag inzet voor advies of opleiding of voor een combinatie van beide. De kosten die in aanmerking komen voor subsidie via de kmo-portefeuille zijn <strong>altijd exclusief btw</strong>. De btw betaalt u rechtstreeks aan de dienstverlener.</p><ul><li>Kleine ondernemingen krijgen 30% steun binnen het jaarlijks steunplafond van 7.500 euro.</li><li>Middelgrote ondernemingen krijgen 20% steun binnen het jaarlijks steunplafond van 7.500 euro.</li></ul><div data-table><table><tbody><tr><td> </td><td>Opleiding of advies</td></tr><tr><td>Kleine ondernemingen</td><td>steunpercentage 30%, steunplafond 7.500 euro (sinds 1 januari 2020)</td></tr><tr><td>Middelgrote ondernemingen</td><td>steunpercentage 20%, steunplafond 7.500 euro (sinds 1 januari 2020)</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>De <strong>aanvaardbare kostprijs</strong> van e